txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.

Wanted: Soft skin from the beasts and lizard-like creatures in the lands west of the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul at the outpost on the shores of Lake Evendim.
'I will see that these are given to those who can put them to good use.'
'Though supplies are not diminished too much, thus far, it is good to prepare for the future. We could use skins from the beasts or lizard-like creatures to the west.'
Wardens of Ann√∫minas Task: Soft Skin
Tinnudir, a Ranger-outpost on the eastern shore of Lake Evendim, is home to the Rangers of Evendim. There, at the outpost, a Ranger named Astiul awaits the return of soft skin.
Deliver the soft skin to Astiul at the Ranger-outpost of Tinnudir
You have been tasked with collecting soft skin from the beasts and lizard-like creatures to the west of Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul within the lakeside outpost.
Wanted: Soft skin from the beasts and lizard-like creatures in the lands west of the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir.
